OL,7,FJon heads up the Mines Advisory
OL,8,FGroup's de-mining task force in
OL,9,FUkraine.
OL,11,FThe delicate process is also combating
OL,12,Ffood insecurity for the poorest people
OL,13,Facross the world.
OL,15,FThe UK government's Foreign
OL,16,FCommonwealth & Development Office says
OL,17,Ftwo years on from Russia's full-scale
OL,18,Finvasion, Ukraine has overtaken Iraq
OL,19,Fand Afghanistan to become the most
OL,20,Fheavily mined country on the planet.
