OL,7,F"Since this war erupted, the price of
OL,8,Fa loaf of bread has probably gone up
OL,9,F10 or 20 pence in the UK. If you think
OL,10,Fhow British people are feeling the
OL,11,Fpinch from the cost-of-living crisis,
OL,12,Fin the world's poorest countries, that
OL,13,Fincrease in price is even more
OL,14,Fdevastating.
OL,16,F"People are suffering worldwide from
OL,17,Fincreased grain prices because
OL,18,FUkraine's agricultural land is strewn
OL,19,Fwith landmines and unexploded ordnance
OL,20,Fso too dangerous to farm.
