OL,7,FManchester-based MAG and Scottish de-
OL,8,Fmining charity The HALO Trust have
OL,9,Fbeen using #11.6million of UK
OL,10,FGovernment funding to bring land mined
OL,11,Fby Russian forces back into productive
OL,12,Fuse.
OL,14,FMinister for Development and Africa,
OL,15,FAndrew Mitchell, said: "Landmines are
OL,16,Fa nightmare ` causing thousands of
OL,17,Fdeaths and injuries each year.
