OL,7,F"The UK remains committed in its
OL,8,Fdetermination to work towards a mine-
OL,9,Ffree world and is delighted to award
OL,10,Fextra funding to MAG and The HALO
OL,11,FTrust to continue their life-saving
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,F"We want to help both organisations
OL,15,Fcreate safe and secure environments
OL,16,Fwhere communities live freely without
OL,17,Ffear of the deadly threat of
OL,18,Flandmines."
